    "After deployment schemes and configurations are generated, these are subjected to simulation and test within the digital twin.",
    "This virtual space enables rigorous test without impacting the physical network.",
    "The simulation phase is critical for identifying potential issues and verifying that the function and configuration meet the intended goals.",
    "The digital twin can refine the configuration via iterative test to ensure its robustness and efficiency.",
    "A feedback mechanism is integral to this process to obtain continuous insights into the configuration performance and perform real-time adjustments and finetuning."
  ],
